、核心特征总结；不得出现英文、拼音、乱码或错字\nConstraints: all text must be simplified Chinese characters only — no English, no pinyin, no garbled characters, no typos; layout must strictly follow the five-zone structure described in Composition; central figure must be full-body standing pose; all annotations must use clean leader lines pointing to correct structural parts; material swatches must be realistic; the overall feel must be 国家博物馆展板 / 历史服饰图鉴 / 文博专题信息图\nAvoid: poster aesthetic, photo-studio aesthetic, e-commerce aesthetic, anime/illustration aesthetic, cosplay aesthetic, incorrect structural annotations, blurry or unreadable text, fake or over-stylized material textures, excessive decorative elements, English text, pinyin, garbled characters",
