k names 断桥残雪, 雷峰塔, 灵隐寺, 飞来峰, 法喜寺, 宋城, 九溪十八涧, 龙井村, 云栖竹径, 西溪湿地 as pin labels on map\\nConstraints: trifold must be legible as a physical printed object; West Lake must be geographically recognizable on the map layer; landmark icons must carry visual identity (pagoda silhouette for 雷峰塔, temple gate for 灵隐寺, bamboo grove for 云栖竹径, tea fields for 龙井村); brochure floats with visible depth above cardstock\\nAvoid: generic flat tourist poster without map context; distorted map geography; overcrowded illegible text; neon or nightclub color palette; 3D render plastic look; watermark\", \"size\": \"1792x1008\", \"quality\": \"medium\", \"n\": 1, \"output_format\": \"png\"}",
