      "final_prompt": {
        "prompt": "Create an original, non-infringing e-commerce landing page hero section UI mockup for a skincare brand called \"LUMEA BEAUTY\", feminine Japanese beauty market.\n\nStyle/medium: clean flat UI mockup, bright and airy editorial layout, feminine aesthetic with floral accents (purple flowers), soft diffused lighting, Figma/Sketch design presentation style\nComposition: full-width desktop landing page hero section, three-column layout — left copy column, center model column, right product column — with a bottom benefit bar; generous white space throughout\nSubject: complete hero section mockup with the following structure —\n\nHEADER: logo wordmark \"LUMEA BEAUTY\" on the left; 5 navigation links reading \"特徴\" / \"成分\" / \"お客様の声\" / \"使い方\" / \"FAQ\"; CTA button reading \"今すぐ試す\" on the right\n\nLEFT COLUMN:\n• Headline (large display type): \"鏡を見るたび、うるおう透明感。\"\n• Subheadline (body text): \"乾燥・くすみが気になる肌に。美容成分を贅沢に配合した、毎日のための集中保湿美容液。\"\n• 3 pill-shaped feature badges with small icons: \"敏感肌OK\" / \"高保湿\" / \"朝晩使える\"\n• 3 bullet points with pink checkmark icons: \"美容成分をしっかり届ける\" / \"ハリ・ツヤのある印象へ\" / \"続けやすいシンプルケア\"\n• 2 CTA buttons: primary filled \"初回限定で試してみる >\" and secondary outline \"成分をチェック >\"\n• Trust badge strip: \"送料無料 / 初回限定 / 定期縛りなし\"\n\nCENTER COLUMN: photorealistic young East Asian woman smiling and touching her cheek with one hand, other hand holding a dropper bottle of serum; soft studio lighting; model blends naturally into the page background\n\nRIGHT COLUMN:\n• 2 product renders — a moisturizing boost serum dropper bottle and its packaging box, clean white background\n• 3 floating white rounded-rectangle stat cards with gold accent details: \"満足度 96%\" / \"美容成分 5種配合\" / \"愛用者 12,000人突破\"\n\nBOTTOM SECTION: 3 horizontal white rounded-rectangle benefit cards with icons: \"うるおい\" / \"透明感\" / \"使いやすさ\"\n\nScene/backdrop: pure white page background with soft pink and white color palette; scattered subtle purple flower illustrations as decorative accents in corners and around the model\nLighting/mood: soft, even, airy — no harsh shadows; warm-neutral light on model's face; overall mood is fresh, trustworthy, and approachable\nColor palette: soft pink as primary brand color, white as base, purple flower accents, gold only on stat card details; typography in near-black for readability\nMaterials/textures: smooth matte UI surfaces, glossy dropper bottle with subtle specular highlight, soft fabric-like skin texture on model\nText (verbatim): \"LUMEA BEAUTY\", \"特徴\", \"成分\", \"お客様の声\", \"使い方\", \"FAQ\", \"今すぐ試す\", \"鏡を見るたび、うるおう透明感。\", \"乾燥・くすみが気になる肌に。美容成分を贅沢に配合した、毎日のための集中保湿美容液。\", \"敏感肌OK\", \"高保湿\", \"朝晩使える\", \"美容成分をしっかり届ける\", \"ハリ・ツヤのある印象へ\", \"続けやすいシンプルケア\", \"初回限定で試してみる >\", \"成分をチェック >\", \"送料無料 / 初回限定 / 定期縛りなし\", \"満足度 96%\", \"美容成分 5種配合\", \"愛用者 12,000人突破\", \"うるおい\", \"透明感\", \"使いやすさ\"\nConstraints: all Japanese text must be legible and correctly rendered; layout must read as a realistic, production-ready desktop landing page mockup; three-column hero grid must be clearly distinguishable; stat cards must appear to float above the product column; pill badges and checkmark bullets must be visually distinct UI components\nAvoid: dark backgrounds, neon colors, masculine aesthetic, cluttered layout, lorem ipsum placeholder text, generic stock-photo flatlay, missing navigation elements, distorted Japanese characters",
